text: Neuenmarkt is a municipality in Kulmbach in Bavaria in Germany. ==City arrangement== Neuenmarkt is arranged in the following boroughs: * Brandhaus * Eichmühle * Hegnabrunn * Lettenhof * Neuenmarkt * Oberlangenroth * Raasen * Reutlashof * Schlömen * See * Unterlangenroth ==References== Category:Kulmbach (district)
title: Neuenmarkt
